---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Cookie Policy" description="Cookie policy for lastseason.co.uk" canonical="/cookies/">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    </section>
    <section class="section prose">
      <p>Last updated: 20 July 2026</p>
      <p>The archive works without analytics cookies. On your first visit, you can allow or reject optional analytics.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Preference storage</h2>
      <p>Your choice is stored in your browser's local storage as <code>lastseason-analytics-choice</code>. This is used only to remember whether analytics may load.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Analytics cookies</h2>
      <p>If you select “Allow analytics”, Google Analytics 4 is loaded to measure aggregate page usage. If you reject it, the analytics script is not loaded by Last Season.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Advertising</h2>
      <p>No advertising network is currently loaded by Last Season, so the site does not intentionally set advertising cookies.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Managing cookies</h2>
      <p>You can clear site data in your browser to reset the choice. The consent panel will be shown again on your next visit. You can also block or delete cookies through browser settings.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
